snippet.title: Total War: ROME II - Empire Divided Trailer
snippet.description:
The year is 270 AD. A string of inept emperors and usurpers vying for power has led the Roman Empire into near-total economic collapse. This is its gravest crisis yet, this is an Empire Divided.
